Package: clex
Type: Package
Title: Statistical downscaling of monthly climate data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christian Zang
Maintainer: Christian Zang <christian.zang@wzw.tum.de>
Description: Extract and downscale climate data from various sources to WorldClim resolution.
  This statistical downscaling approach follows Mosier et al. 2014 Int. J. Climatol.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
  ncdf4,
  sp,
  raster,
  tidyr,
  rlang
Suggests:
  parallel
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
